{"image_id": "SBAC_2012_page_122", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 90.1, 206.4, 118.8]}, {"text": "SBA COMMUNICATIONS CORPORATION AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [329.7, 142.2, 955.7, 171.1]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS", "bbox": [362.0, 165.2, 923.4, 194.1]}, {"text": "Employee Stock Purchase Plan", "bbox": [37.5, 205.7, 316.9, 234.2]}, {"text": "In 2008, the Board of Directors of the Company adopted the 2008 Employee Stock Purchase Plan (“2008 Purchase Plan”) which reserved", "bbox": [85.5, 238.2, 1239.2, 265.8]}, {"text": "500,000 shares of Class A common stock for purchase. The 2008 Purchase Plan permits eligible employee participants to purchase Class A", "bbox": [37.5, 261.2, 1204.4, 288.8]}, {"text": "common stock at a price per share which is equal to 85% of the fair market value of Class A common stock on the last day of an offering", "bbox": [37.5, 284.2, 1184.7, 311.8]}, {"text": "period.", "bbox": [37.5, 307.4, 106.4, 335.1]}, {"text": "For the year ended December 31, 2012, 23,724 shares of Class A common stock were issued under the 2008 Purchase Plan, which", "bbox": [85.5, 349.2, 1177.9, 376.8]}, {"text": "resulted in cash proceeds to the Company of approximately $1.1 million compared to the year ended December 31, 2011 when approximately", "bbox": [37.5, 372.2, 1225.2, 399.8]}, {"text": "30,942 shares of Class A common stock were issued under the 2008 Purchase Plan, which resulted in cash proceeds to the Company of $1.0", "bbox": [37.5, 395.2, 1211.4, 422.8]}, {"text": "million. At December 31, 2012, 380,045 shares remained available for issuance under the 2008 Purchase Plan. In addition, the Company", "bbox": [37.5, 418.4, 1183.2, 446.1]}, {"text": "recorded $0.2 million of non-cash compensation expense relating to the shares issued under the 2008 Purchase Plans for each of the years", "bbox": [37.5, 441.4, 1190.4, 469.1]}, {"text": "ended December 31, 2012, 2011, and 2010.", "bbox": [37.5, 464.4, 411.2, 492.1]}, {"text": "Non-Cash Compensation Expense", "bbox": [37.5, 515.7, 342.9, 544.2]}, {"text": "The table below reflects a break out by category of the non-cash compensation expense amounts recognized on the Company’s", "bbox": [85.5, 548.2, 1149.4, 575.8]}, {"text": "Statements of Operations for the years ended December 31, 2012, 2011, and 2010, respectively:", "bbox": [37.5, 571.2, 847.9, 598.8]}, {"text": "In addition, the Company capitalized $0.2 million, $0.2 million and $0.1 million of non-cash compensation for the years ended", "bbox": [85.5, 853.7, 1148.9, 881.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2012, 2011 and 2010, respectively, to fixed and intangible assets.", "bbox": [37.5, 876.9, 714.4, 904.6]}, {"text": "Loss before provision for income taxes from continuing operations by geographic area is as follows:", "bbox": [85.5, 963.4, 932.4, 991.1]}, {"text": "F-47", "bbox": [617.7, 1160.7, 662.4, 1188.3]}, {"text": "For the year ended December 31,", "bbox": [860.7, 617.3, 1087.7, 639.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [835.7, 636.3, 871.2, 658.1]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [956.2, 636.3, 991.7, 658.1]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1077.0, 636.3, 1112.4, 658.1]}, {"text": "(in thousands, except per share amounts)", "bbox": [834.5, 654.6, 1113.9, 676.4]}, {"text": "Cost of revenues", "bbox": [133.5, 683.7, 278.7, 711.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [813.0, 683.7, 828.7, 711.3]}, {"text": "187", "bbox": [858.5, 683.7, 913.2, 711.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [933.7, 683.7, 949.4, 711.3]}, {"text": "187", "bbox": [979.0, 683.7, 1033.9, 711.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1054.5, 683.7, 1070.2, 711.3]}, {"text": "189", "bbox": [1099.7, 683.7, 1146.7, 711.3]}, {"text": "Selling, general and administrative", "bbox": [133.5, 706.7, 429.2, 734.3]}, {"text": "13,781", "bbox": [818.2, 706.7, 913.2, 734.3]}, {"text": "11,282", "bbox": [939.0, 706.7, 1033.9, 734.3]}, {"text": "10,312", "bbox": [1059.7, 706.7, 1146.7, 734.3]}, {"text": "Total cost of non-cash compensation i